{
  "texts": [
    "This study focuses on two specific challenges to reduce the development costs while closely considering user feedback:• (P1) A method is needed to understand the new services desired by users; • (P2) It is necessary to discover methods that simplify the development of new services.For (P1), it is essential to identify what services should be developed by understanding the specific services each enduser desires.",
    "Particularly, it is important to determine how to elicit details about unknown services from users and clarify their needs for new services.",
    "In (P2), the aim is to discover development methods related to realizing the service needs identified.",
    "This involves clarifying whether the targeted service development is feasible or challenging and what specific implementation methods are available.",
    "Especially, it is crucial to understand what technologies can be employed to realize the services and functionalities users desire."
  ]
}